<graph edgedefault="undirected"><node id="&quot;IMAGE_4_PERSON-0.JPG&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"IMG"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The category of this image feature block is 'person'. The entity features are as follows:Person Features:- **Gender:** Indeterminate from this angle and resolution, but appears to be an adult.- **Hairstyle:** Not visible, as the head is covered by a hood.- **Clothing:** Wearing a dark-colored, likely gray or black, hooded jacket or sweatshirt. The hood is pulled up, covering the head. The fabric appears somewhat thick, suggesting a warm garment. Below the jacket, a darker, possibly black, lower garment (trousers or skirt) is visible.- **Posture:** The person is seen from the back, appearing to be standing or walking away. The head is slightly bowed or looking forward.- **Age:** Appears to be an adult, but more specific age estimation is not possible due to the lack of visible facial features or distinguishing characteristics."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_4.jpg</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;IMAGE_4_PERSON-1.JPG&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"IMG"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The category of this image feature block is 'person'. The entity features are as follows:Person Features:- **Gender:** Appears to be female.- **Hairstyle:** Long, dark hair, seemingly pulled back or styled, visible from the side profile.- **Clothing:** Wearing a dark, short-sleeved top (possibly a t-shirt or athletic jersey) and dark shorts. There appears to be a lighter colored band or stripe on the upper right arm.- **Facial Expression:** The face is mostly obscured as the person is in a side profile with the head tilted downwards. No clear expression is discernible.- **Age:** Appears to be an adult or older youth.- **Posture:** The person is in an athletic stance, leaning forward with knees slightly bent. Both arms are extended forward and slightly upwards, with hands together, suggesting an action like receiving or hitting a ball (e.g., in volleyball).- **Overall Impression:** The pose indicates active participation in a sport or physical activity. The image is black and white."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_4.jpg</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;IMAGE_4_PERSON-3.JPG&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"IMG"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The category of this image feature block is 'person'. The entity features are as follows:Person Features:- **Gender:** Indeterminate from the silhouette, but the broad shoulders might suggest a male figure.- **Hairstyle:** Appears to have short hair, but specific details are not discernible due to the silhouette.- **Clothing:** Seems to be wearing a top with a collar, possibly a jacket or a collared shirt, with distinct shoulder lines.- **Facial Expression:** Not discernible.- **Age:** Not discernible from the silhouette.- **Posture:** The person is depicted from the chest up, with both arms extended outwards and slightly upwards from the torso. The head is turned slightly to the viewer's left. The pose suggests an action, possibly gesturing, reaching, or holding something.- **Overall Appearance:** A dark, low-resolution silhouette of a person's upper body, indicating a dynamic posture."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_4.jpg</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;IMAGE_4&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"ORI_IMG"</data>
  <data key="d1">"The image is a black and white photograph depicting an indoor scene, likely a museum or visitor center, with a large, prominent spherical water feature at its center. The sphere is dark, highly polished, and appears to be made of stone or metal, with water visibly cascading down its surface and collecting in a circular, textured basin below. On the right side of the sphere, a young child, possibly a boy, is interacting with it, reaching out with both hands to touch its smooth, wet surface. The child is wearing a light-colored, possibly checkered, short-sleeved top, light-colored shorts, and a dark baseball cap. Their posture suggests curiosity and engagement with the exhibit. In the background, several other people are visible, some standing, some observing other exhibits, suggesting a public and educational environment. The lighting in the room is ambient, with some overhead light sources creating reflections on the sphere. The overall atmosphere is calm and educational, focusing on the interaction between the child and the unique water sculpture."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_4.jpg</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;GIRL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"PERSON"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A young girl, seen from the side, wearing a hat, a dark short-sleeved shirt, and light-colored shorts or pants. She is actively touching a large dark sphere with both hands, looking engaged and curious."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_4.jpg</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;LARGE SPHERE&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A prominent, very large, dark, glossy spherical object, appearing to be made of stone or polished granite. It is positioned on a cylindrical base, with water visibly flowing around its lower portion, suggesting it's a kinetic water sculpture or globe."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_4.jpg</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;PEDESTAL&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"A sturdy, cylindrical base made of a light-colored, textured material, possibly stone or concrete. It supports the large dark sphere and contains the water feature."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_4.jpg</data>
</node>
<node id="&quot;WATER&quot;">
  <data key="d0">"OBJECT"</data>
  <data key="d1">"Visible as a thin sheet or stream flowing outwards from beneath the large sphere and over the edge of the pedestal, indicating a water fountain or kinetic sculpture."</data>
  <data key="d2">C:/MMGraphRAG/MMGraphRAG/test_runs/api_working\images\image_4.jpg</data>
</node>
